cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CR 

This paper deals with image classification and the robustness of neural networks to common corruptions and surface variations. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses ways to enhance robustness, which falls under the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a new dataset, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper discusses the importance of safety-critical applications, which could fall under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
